nodes.bodyText: @keithc-ca is this called during an OpenJ9 run?  If we don't expect it to be (and why would it if it's CDS related), it would be better to assert here

There are still some more changes required to openj9 to create a build against the openj9-staging branch of jdknext. My first observation was a link error referring to this function, but a closer look at how it's used suggests it is required beyond support for CDS and that our implementation should just return zero. I'll update it to do that.
